<div class="block block--info js-info-box-container">
<div class="block__header">
<h3 class="block__title h3 js-info-box-trigger" data-state="off">Loan Policies</h3>
</div>
<div class="js-block-info-content-container block__content cms" style="display: none;">
<p>The J.W. Tate Library is open for use by the general public. A valid university photo identification card must be presented for all library transactions. Library cards are obtained from the Desmarais Library at Laurentian University.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="block block--info js-info-box-container">
<div class="block__header">
