<div class="block block--info js-info-box-container">
<div class="block__header">
<h3 class="block__title h3 js-info-box-trigger" data-state="off">Return Procedures</h3>
</div>
<div class="js-block-info-content-container block__content cms" style="display: none;">
<p>All J.W. Tate material must be returned to the library circulation desk or placed in the book drop outside the library. Material should not be returned to other campus libraries.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="block block--info js-info-box-container">
<div class="block__header">
<h3 class="block__title h3 js-info-box-trigger" data-state="off">Renewals</h3>
</div>
<div class="js-block-info-content-container block__content cms" style="display: none;">
<p>All items may be renewed up to three times in-person or through the online library system so long as another patron has not requested the item.</p><div class='mailmunch-forms-in-post-middle' style='display: none !important;'></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="block block--info js-info-box-container">
<div class="block__header">
<h3 class="block__title h3 js-info-box-trigger" data-state="off">Recalls and Holds</h3>
</div>
<div class="js-block-info-content-container block__content cms" style="display: none;">
<p>Patrons can place a hold on a book currently checked out. The book will be held for three days. All checked out items are subject to recall if requested by another borrower. Patrons will be given one week to return the book after which time they will be charged $2 a day.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="block block--info js-info-box-container">
<div class="block__header">
<h3 class="block__title h3 js-info-box-trigger" data-state="off">Fines</h3>
</div>
<div class="js-block-info-content-container block__content cms" style="display: none;">
<p>Fines for a regular loan item are $0.50 per day to a maximum of $15.00. Patrons may not sign out items if they have $10 in fines or more.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="block block--info js-info-box-container">
<div class="block__header">
<h3 class="block__title h3 js-info-box-trigger" data-state="off">Hours of Operation</h3>
</div>
<div class="js-block-info-content-container block__content cms" style="display: none;">
<p><strong>Winter 2015</strong><br />
Monday: 10-6pm<br />
Tuesday: 10-9pm<br />
Wednesday: 10-9pm<br />
